  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "In the latest 2.1 spec. Attestation slot validity rule has changed from referencing \"current_slot\" to \"parent_slot\".\r\n\r\nBefore:\r\n```\r\nif not (slot <= current.slot_number and slot >= max(current.slot_number - CYCLE_LENGTH + 1, 0)) {\r\n   throw error\r\n}\r\n```\r\nNow:\r\n```\r\nif not (slot <= parent.slot_number and slot >= max(parent.slot_number - CYCLE_LENGTH + 1, 0)) {\r\n   throw error\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nHere's where the change should happen: https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/master/beacon-chain/blockchain/core.go#L244",
